longBusinessSummary: Evergreen Gaming Corporation engages in the gaming operations in the United States. It operates Riverside casino in Tukwila; Goldies Casino in Shoreline; and Chips and Palace casinos in Lakewood. The company's casinos offer card games, such as Poker, Blackjack, Spanish 21, 4-Card Poker, PaiGow, and Baccarat; and pull tabs, a game in which the player can win specified prizes by matching certain combinations concealed under perforated strips on each paper game piece. It also operates bars and restaurants in its casinos. The company is based in Lakewood, Washington.
